data.description: Exceptionally maintained upper condo unit with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms overlooking the communal space! This charming residence boasts abundant natural light and showcases a well-appointed kitchen with elegant granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The included washer and dryer add to the convenience of this lovely home. You'll also find a spacious dining room, recently updated carpeting, a generously sized guest bedroom, a full guest bathroom, and a luxurious owner's suite complete with a private en-suite 3/4 bathroom. Enjoy coffee outside on the covered 6 x16 rear patio or the front porch! Amenities include Pool, fitness room, game room, clubhouse and trails!
